like a big shadow.

1004
01:03:22.548 --> 01:03:24.841
Let me tell you something
you already know.

1005
01:03:25.009 --> 01:03:27.344
The world ain't all
sunshine and rainbows.

1006
01:03:27.512 --> 01:03:31.348
It's a very mean and nasty place,
and I don't care how tough you are,

1007
01:03:31.516 --> 01:03:35.101
