because of him or her or anybody!

1016
01:04:02.630 --> 01:04:06.883
Cowards do that, and that ain't you!
You're better than that!

1017
01:04:07.093 --> 01:04:09.094
[♪♪♪]

1018
01:04:13.599 --> 01:04:16.935
I'm always gonna love you
no matter what.

1019
01:04:17.103 --> 01:04:18.979
No matter what happens.

1020
01:04:19.355 --> 01:04:22.148
You're my son
and you're my blood.

1021
01:04:22.316 --> 01:04:25.110
You're the best thing in my life.

1022
01:04:26.320 --> 01:04:30.198
But until you start believing in
yourself, you ain't gonna have a life.

1023
01:04:35.037 --> 01:04:37.539
Don't forget to visit your mother.

1024
01:05:20.082 --> 01:05:21.917
[♪♪♪]

1025
01:05:27.423 --> 01:05:30.050
Yeah, those are beautiful.
Yeah.

1026
01:05:32.011 --> 01:05:35.096
